Acceptance: SRS-NFR-03/AC-01

Compression remains storage-only. Logical payload bytes, offsets, replay order, and hosted read/tail semantics are unchanged after rolled history is decoded through the shared engine.

Evidence:
- `cargo test -p transit-core rolled_segments_store_compressed_bytes_and_replay_original_records`
- `cargo test -p transit-core remote_append_read_and_tail_preserve_positions_and_branch_aware_replay_behavior`

